data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home located on a peaceful cul-de-sac in a desirable Broken Arrow neighborhood! This spacious property boasts 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a total of 2,091 square feet of living space. As you enter the home, you'll be greeted by a cozy living room featuring a beautiful fireplace, perfect for creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to the dining area and kitchen, providing an ideal space for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen is well-appointed with modern appliances, ample cabinet space, and a convenient breakfast bar. It's a chef's delight, allowing you to whip up delicious meals with ease. One of the standout features of this property is the inclusion of a safe room, offering peace of mind during severe weather events or as a secure storage space. The master suite is a true retreat, providing a relaxing haven with its generous size and en-suite bathroom. The three additional bedrooms are spacious and versatile, allowing for various uses such as a home office, gym, or guest rooms. Step outside and discover the lovely enclosed patio and porch, where you can enjoy your morning coffee or unwind after a long day. The .21-acre lot is beautifully landscaped and features a privacy fence, creating a serene and secluded ambiance. This home also offers a two-car garage, ensuring plenty of space for parking and storage. The wood-frame construction adds to the timeless appeal of the property. Additional features include a programmable thermostat, allowing you to efficiently control the temperature and save on energy costs throughout the year. New A/C, Furnace and Water Heater. In summary, this 4 bedroom, 2 bath ranch-style home offers a comfortable and inviting living space, enhanced by its thoughtful features such as the fireplace, safe room, enclosed patio, and privacy fence. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful property your own!
